# Welcome to Rocksolid
This is a custom ROM currently for the Nexus 4 and 7. This ROM is the most customization ROM ever. I will be creating 3 different ROMS for the Current Release. (Due to internet problem this won't be up until tomorrow.) 

## Release 1
*All Google Apps
*Clockworkmod
*Chrome is default browser
_Very user Friendly_ 

## Release 2
*All Google Apps
*Root Explorer
*Titanium Backup
_Very Developer Friendly_
 
## Release 3
*No Google Apps( Must download by yourself)
*Default Android Experience
_Very Bare Experience_
